column3: “Chocolaty taste & smell, dark in color. Super head high. Great for not doing much.”
“made bho out of this trippy man trippy!”

“strong head high
cerebral and good for music”

“Tasty - herbal/clean taste - earthy - mushroom - $soapy$  
Confused, paranoid, semi-focused, happy, chill”
“Clear and strong, a fun ride with focus. Good for tv. Good daytime meds.”
“A pretty mellow strain that makes me feel happy. A good daytime high where you can still get things done”

“Very nice head high, a bit jittery with morning coffee, but gets you into a focused  work mode and keeps you there for a long while. A classic sativa with lots of punch, great pain control and clarity.”

“This is the best strain I've had in a minute. I love this I'm so relaxed and happy and I'm focused so it's great for work.  It's is also great for night time for relaxing and taking a bath or watching Netflix then falling asleep. It tastes like chocolate and is kind of spicy. I get a good head high but I'm focused. I love this strain.😍😍”
